<HEADLINE>
<P>
PUT ASTROLOGY IN ITS PLACE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Congratulations. You have finally found the right place for the astrological 
forecasts -- next to the comics. I admit I occasionally read them, for 
something to laugh at. 
</P>
<P>
Even among the strange people who take them seriously, there are those who find 
grave faults with them. The few that may some day be taken seriously are those 
who base their expectations on the astrological arrangements in the sky at the 
precise moment of birth. 
</P>
<P>
ROBERT HARDING, Northridge 
</P>
