<P>
TOYS R US BUYS RIALTO SITE FOR DISTRIBUTION CENTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Toys R Us has acquired a 50-acre parcel of industrial land in Rialto for more 
than $5 million and plans to build a regional distribution center on the site. 
</P>
<P>
The property is located at the northeast corner of Cedar and Merrill avenues. 
Handling the transaction were the Seeley Co.'s San Gabriel Valley office on 
behalf of the seller, Shadrall Associates of Massachusetts; L.J. Hooker Co. of 
San Diego represented Toys R Us. 
</P>
