CHEROKEE AVE. APARTMENTS SOLD FOR $3.01 MILLION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The apartment complex at 1215-25 N. Cherokee Ave. has been sold by Yom 
Development and Cherokee HO3 Ltd. of Los Angeles for $3.01 million, according 
to the Hanes Co. Inc., Los Angeles region, brokers in the transaction. 
</P>
