<TEXT>
<P>
Dale Dowers has been named president of Costain Homes Inc., a Newport 
Beach-based home builder active throughout Riverside and San Bernardino 
counties. The company is a division of Costain Group PLC which has a worldwide 
operation in engineering and construction, mining, real estate property 
investment/management and housing. 
</P>
