Great Britain's Barratt Developments PLC has appointed Mark Frazier chairman of 
Barratt American. Frazier will also serve on the main board of the Barratt 
Group. Based in Irvine, the firm has building projects in Orange, San Diego, 
Riverside and San Bernardino counties. 
</P>
