Bruce T. Lehman has joined Akins Development Co. as senior vice president and 
chief financial officer. Lehman will oversee the coordination and maintenance 
of all corporate information and direct the company's day-to-day business. 
Headquartered in Newport Beach, Akins has residential building programs in 
Orange County and the Inland Empire. 
