The Sickels Group, headquartered in San Diego, has named Lee A. Gibbs vice 
president of retail development and Philip S. Gorgone vice president of 
residential development. Gibbs will direct the company's statewide effort to 
identify and acquire existing shopping centers and land for new retail 
developments, while Gorgone will direct efforts toward developing new apartment 
communities. 
