Elliott Corp. has elevated directors Larry Combs and Gary Monroe to vice 
presidents. Combs will be in charge of all construction operations and field 
staff, while Monroe will oversee the project management staff, as well as the 
estimating operations. The company is located in Newport Beach. 
</P>
