Martin A. Ensbury has become vice president of marketing for Westgroup 
Partners, a Los Angeles-based firm which renovates vintage office and hotel 
structures in downtown areas. Ensbury will be responsible for the marketing and 
leasing activities for One Bunker Hill. 
