<HEADLINE>
<P>
MISSION VIEJO RECALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
We hold no brief for City Councilman (Robert A.) Curtis of Mission Viejo, but 
we do resent the fact that the Mission Viejo Co., William Lyon Co. and Baldwin 
Co. are trying to buy his recall with money and a paid political consultant. 
All these companies are interested in is profit, and they'll let no one stand 
in their way. 
</P>
<P>
It's bad enough that every hill and gully in Mission Viejo is covered with 
their ticky-tacky houses; they only want to make it worse! 
</P>
<P>
RAY KOVITZ 
</P>
<P>
Mission Viejo 
</P>
</TEXT>
