swept, 15-7, 15-12. Jolie Eberhart had seven kills for Golden West. 
</P>
<P>
Golden West 3, Scottsdale 1 -- In the quarterfinal match, Golden West (2-2) 
defeated Scottsdale, 10-15, 15-12, 15-6, 15-8. 
</P>
