lot in Torrance when they meet monthly. ; Photo, Kim Allen, 2, loves cars 
already. His father brought him and the gas-powered 4x2 Coyote to the Torrance 
Cruisin' '50's meeting along with his own '57 Chevy Nomad. ; Photo, Mike and 
Carolyn Indovina's 1929 Model A Ford street rod has cost them $60,000 -- so 
far. PATRICK DOWNS / Los Angeles Times; Photo, California's passion for the 
automobile has brought with it a pall of smog in this view of downtown Los 
Angeles looking west. ELLEN JASKOL / Los Angeles Times; Photo, (Bulldog 
