</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA100189-0187 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 114922 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 1, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
