POLAND -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- WEST GERMANY; WEST GERMANY -- IMMIGRATION; EAST 
GERMANY -- EMIGRATION; EAST GERMANY -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- WEST GERMANY 
</P>
