NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Boston Celtics star Larry Bird was married to Dinah Mattingly of Indianapolis 
in a private ceremony, the manager of Bird's restaurant in Terre Haute, Ind., 
said. 
</P>
<P>
The ceremony took place at the home of Terre Haute businessman Max Gibson, 
according to Glen Ankney. Bird, Gibson and Ankney are partners in a Terre Haute 
hotel-restaurant complex called Larry Bird's Boston Connection. 
</P>
